author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
This week, we explore the MCU designs of the Fantastic Four with Marvel Studios Executive Creative Director and Production Illustrator, Ryan Meinerding. We also hear from the President of Trading Cards for Fanatics Collectibles David Leiner on what fans can expect from the 2025 Topps Chrome Marvel launch. Plus, writer Benjamin Percy tells us about Frank Castle’s return to Marvel Comics in Punisher: Red Band #1. All time codes are approximate.

00:00 - Welcome Back!
1:09 -  Marvel Studios Executive Creative Director and Production Illustrator, Ryan Meinerding talks the F4's MCU designs
12:00 - President of Trading Cards for Fanatics Collectibles David Leiner on the Topps Chrome Marvel launch
21:05 - Writer Benjamin Percy on Frank Castle's return in Punisher: Red Band #1
